Notes: WIAC semifinal round... UWO's Mikolajczak scored nine of team's first 11
points to begin the second half... UWO led 43-39 and went on 17-4 run over
next 6:32 to take 60-43 lead... SP followed with 11-1 run to cut lead to
61-55, but UWO nine of 11 free throws in final 1:09 to seal the win.
Game.Officials: Lou Pitt,  Bernie Barribeau,  Becky Blank
